				)
			)
		)
		(property "Description" "Pimoroni Pico LiPo 2 (PIM775) — RP2350B-based Pico-form-factor development board with USB‑C, onboard LiPo/LiIon charging and protection, and a Pico-compatible 40-pin header. Provides regulated 3.3V rail and exposes standard Pico power pins (VBUS, VSYS, 3V3). Includes power-enable control via 3V3_EN (tied to the board’s POWER_EN logic), RUN reset input, and ADC reference pin. Board includes MCP73831 charger, XB6096I2S battery protection, onboard 3V3 regulator (up to ~600mA), plus user/power/charge indicators and onboard connectors (Qw/ST, SP/CE, debug)."
			(at -50.8 96.52 0)
			(show_name no)
			(do_not_autoplace no)
			(hide yes)
